TION> Cebu </LOCATION>. In another development, President <PERSON> Corazon </PERSON> <PERSON> Aquino </PERSON> today pardoned or shortened sentences for 155 convicts as part of her government's program to ease extreme punishment for inmates A presidential palace statement said the order included conditional pardons for four convicts, parole for 13 and the commutation of sentences for 138 others. The statement did not say what crimes the prisoners committed.
